skriipts.bmp
`FA bitmap renderer`

`FUSAGE`
	Pass an array of bytes as the parameter `Nd`.

`FCAVEATS`
	Only colors that are supported by hackmud with color codes will be rendered correctly, if the image contains a color that is not supported by hackmud, an allowed color with the closest hue will be used.
	This only supports 8bpp and 24bpp formats with a BITMAPINFOHEADER.
